<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们回到家里把这些金币放进了袋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊和鲍比把所有的金币都放到了一个背包里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么知道哪些是我的呢？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系。”他哥哥回答说，“我们可以一起用啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩们决定把钱分了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘瑟，那是我的金币。”简说着捡起一枚掉到地上的金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，简。那是我的。这是从我的口袋里掉出来的。”潘瑟分辨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从妹妹那里抢过了金币放进自己的袋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们回到镇上之后，都为自己新得到的财富而激动不已。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你先买什么？”鲍比问赛伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要买一百盘游戏，这样我就永远不会感到无聊了。”他回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要买辆车。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼睛里闪着光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不会开车啊！”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比耸耸肩说：“没事儿。我雇个司机给我开就行了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊在一家店门前停下了脚步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们到了！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起他的手指着一块写着“游戏世界”的牌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想去那家店。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不想。”简表示赞同。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去多特服装店看看裙子。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们开始争论应该先去哪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后赛伊举起双手说：“我们可以各自去自己想去的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们买完东西再在这里碰头，好吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他几个孩子马上同意了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊一个人走进了游戏商店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的目光落在一排排游戏碟上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”他屏住了呼吸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能帮你什么忙吗？”店员问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”赛伊回答，“店里每种游戏给我来一套。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比呢？他去看车了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用手指触碰着一辆双门银色跑车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在给爸爸看生日礼物吗？”一个汽车销售员开玩笑说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没准他存上十年的钱就可以买一辆了。”另一个销售员大笑道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很可能要花上二十年的时间。”其他人大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比高高地昂着头离开了这家店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们等着瞧。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和简去了多特服装店买衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩们试了很多件裙子，最后找到了一件她们都喜欢的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“简，那是我的裙子。”潘瑟指着简手里的裙子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那和潘瑟穿在身上的裙子一模一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我的裙子。我先看到的。”简不满地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么不再找一条裙子呢？”潘瑟温柔地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你为什么不再找一条？”简用令人讨厌的语气回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而在游戏商店里，赛伊站在结账柜台前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在清点所有的新游戏。这些很快就都是他的了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看，小朋友。”店员说，“所有的游戏，你要怎么付钱？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可是个非常有钱的人。”赛伊自命不凡地回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许你应该先给我看看你的钱。”店员说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼珠子转来转去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊把装满金币的很重的背包扔到了柜台上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个包里都是钱。”他告诉店员说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊！”鲍比突然跑进了店里说，“我要钱买车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊硬是把鲍比推开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在不行，鲍比。我忙着呢！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我找到我想要的车了！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他试图去抓那个包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊硬是把鲍比挤开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我付完游戏的钱就把包给你！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那也是我的钱！”鲍比大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>